00:03:18.690 --> 00:03:20.740
snooping for information because

00:03:20.920 --> 00:03:22.760
he was worried about his wife and son.

00:03:25.320 --> 00:03:26.540
That worries me.

00:03:27.040 --> 00:03:28.380
