00:03:28.870 --> 00:03:29.610
No.

00:03:29.640 --> 00:03:30.560
It's too dangerous.

00:03:30.710 --> 00:03:32.450
At this point, don't stop me.

00:03:32.640 --> 00:03:33.620
I have to go.

