It's daytime,

00:03:35.060 --> 00:03:36.020
so how will you get there?

00:03:37.670 --> 00:03:38.400
The same way as before.

00:03:38.710 --> 00:03:39.560
As before.

00:03:40.360 --> 00:03:41.120
What will you say then?

00:03:41.920 --> 00:03:42.950
Are you going to ask Sun Siming,

00:03:43.430 --> 00:03:45.190
"Did you see Feng Qianli last night?"

00:03:45.640 --> 00:03:46.510
or

00:03:46.640 --> 00:03:48.280
"Did you catch Meng Qin this morning?"

00:03:48.430 --> 00:03:49.570
I won't say that,

00:03:49.710 --> 00:03:50.750
so I need you to help me.

00:03:52.150 --> 00:03:52.750
Me?

00:03:57.360 --> 00:03:59.950
You want me in the dark while you're in the open?

00:04:00.270 --> 00:04:00.750
Yeah.

00:04:01.360 --> 00:04:02.280
Then I'll go too.

00:04:02.550 --> 00:04:04.470
I'll keep them in check.

00:04:05.360 --> 00:04:06.230
- Let's go.- OK.

00:04:08.870 --> 00:04:09.510
Jiu.

00:04:14.430 --> 00:04:15.510
Did you sleep here last night?

00:04:21.790 --> 00:04:22.840
Do you realize what you did was wrong?

00:04:25.230 --> 00:04:26.160
Jiu.

00:04:26.320 --> 00:04:27.200
Yes.

00:04:27.560 --> 00:04:28.110
Yes.

00:04:28.710 --> 00:04:29.200
Let's go.

