His Excellency is waiting for you at the mansion.

00:04:31.350 --> 00:04:32.160
I can't go.

00:04:37.590 --> 00:04:38.600
By the way, Jiu.

00:04:39.080 --> 00:04:40.430
You're good at fighting,

00:04:40.960 --> 00:04:42.310
so can you do me a small favor?

00:04:48.940 --> 00:04:51.460
[Linrong Umbrella Repairing]

00:05:24.680 --> 00:05:25.660
Are you feeling cold?

00:05:26.170 --> 00:05:26.780
No, I'm not.

00:05:39.560 --> 00:05:40.120
Let's go.

00:05:40.320 --> 00:05:41.130
What are you doing?

00:05:41.470 --> 00:05:42.530
Don't ask. Come on.

00:05:42.530 --> 00:05:43.750
- Come on. - Where are you taking us?

00:05:44.820 --> 00:05:47.940
[Jibei Chamber of Commerce]

00:05:51.680 --> 00:05:52.550
Who are you?

00:05:53.200 --> 00:05:54.960
Please inform Chairman Sun

00:05:55.120 --> 00:05:56.350
that Fu Sheng wants to see him.

00:05:57.200 --> 00:05:58.720
Do you think you can meet him at will?

00:05:58.990 --> 00:06:00.230
Go away.

00:06:01.230 --> 00:06:02.430
Why are you pushing him?

00:06:02.870 --> 00:06:03.680
Do you know who I am?

00:06:03.760 --> 00:06:04.510
Who are you?

00:06:04.870 --> 00:06:06.240
Young Mistress of Xichuan.

00:06:10.310 --> 00:06:11.280
Young Mistress, please forgive me

00:06:11.280 --> 00:06:12.240
for being blind.

00:06:12.470 --> 00:06:13.350
Then call out

00:06:13.350 --> 00:06:14.720
your Chairman Sun now.

00:06:15.040 --> 00:06:16.690
Our Chairman is not here.

00:06:17.040 --> 00:06:17.870
He just went out.

00:06:20.790 --> 00:06:21.800
The Chairman isn't here?

00:06:22.040 --> 00:06:23.070
The Vice Chairman?

00:06:23.400 --> 00:06:24.600
Yes.

00:06:24.600 --> 00:06:25.280
Lead us to her.

00:06:26.350 --> 00:06:27.040
Please.

00:06:27.040 --> 00:06:32.220
[Jibei Chamber of Commerce]

00:06:44.280 --> 00:06:44.990
The dungeon is over there.

00:06:59.110 --> 00:07:01.510
Mother, where are we going?

00:07:02.870 --> 00:07:05.560
Mother, are we going to die?

00:07:06.470 --> 00:07:07.040
No, we're not.

00:07:07.990 --> 00:07:09.920
I will protect you with my life.

00:07:11.490 --> 00:07:12.500
What's going on here?

00:07:12.500 --> 00:07:13.810
What crime

00:07:13.810 --> 00:07:15.460
has a child this young committed?

00:07:16.140 --> 00:07:17.220
I want to know too.

00:07:17.220 --> 00:07:18.460
It's too bad.

00:07:18.460 --> 00:07:18.960
Yes.

00:07:18.960 --> 00:07:20.440
They're pathetic.

00:07:20.440 --> 00:07:21.090
Yeah.

00:07:43.790 --> 00:07:45.190
You've been sitting here for a quarter of an hour

00:07:45.470 --> 00:07:46.420
and haven't said why you're here,

00:07:48.280 --> 00:07:48.990
but that's all right.

00:07:49.550 --> 00:07:50.780
I'm not busy anyway.

00:07:54.080 --> 00:07:56.680
When will Chairman Sun be back?

00:07:57.350 --> 00:07:58.870
Chairman Sun is busy outside,

00:07:59.200 --> 00:08:00.480
so I'm afraid he won't be back for a while.

00:08:01.160 --> 00:08:02.400
Physician Fu, you can

00:08:02.400 --> 00:08:03.280
tell me anything.

00:08:04.400 --> 00:08:05.450
Then we'll wait a little longer.

00:08:07.200 --> 00:08:07.720
No problem.

00:08:08.310 --> 00:08:10.720
Then let's stay for lunch.

00:08:20.840 --> 00:08:22.680
Chairman Guo, what do you mean?

00:08:23.040 --> 00:08:23.920
What can I mean?

00:08:24.670 --> 00:08:25.410
I want to keep my guests,

00:08:25.870 --> 00:08:27.240
so I have to be sincere.

00:08:28.310 --> 00:08:30.070
Young Mistress, you live a good life,

00:08:30.520 --> 00:08:31.600
so you won't be used

00:08:31.600 --> 00:08:32.320
to our humble food.

00:08:32.590 --> 00:08:33.630
You can help yourself,

00:08:34.830 --> 00:08:35.790
but Physician Fu must stay.

00:08:37.070 --> 00:08:38.130
Fu Sheng is my man.

00:08:38.190 --> 00:08:40.030
Since I brought him here, I'll take him away.

00:08:40.430 --> 00:08:42.720
If he doesn't leave, neither will I.

00:08:43.520 --> 00:08:45.600
But I must kindly remind you.

00:08:46.070 --> 00:08:47.640
In Xichuan, everyone knows

00:08:47.640 --> 00:08:48.630
that my father cares about me the most.

00:08:48.830 --> 00:08:50.160
If he knows I am under house arrest

00:08:50.160 --> 00:08:51.910
by the Jibei Chamber of Commerce,

00:08:52.400 --> 00:08:54.120
guess what will happen.

00:08:59.520 --> 00:09:00.600
Fu Sheng, let's go.

00:09:13.590 --> 00:09:15.670
Madam, why are we afraid of Lord's Mansion?

00:09:15.830 --> 00:09:16.960
Wouldn't it be better to detain them

00:09:17.070 --> 00:09:18.910
to force them to hand over the jade plate?

00:09:18.910 --> 00:09:19.960
We haven't got the map yet,

00:09:20.790 --> 00:09:21.990
so we can't turn our backs on them now

00:09:22.040 --> 00:09:23.020
in case something unexpected happens.

00:09:24.000 --> 00:09:25.270
Let's just hold out.

00:09:54.000 --> 00:09:55.150
This is your home.

00:09:58.430 --> 00:09:59.990
Madam, don't be afraid.

00:10:00.280 --> 00:10:01.440
I won't eat you.

00:10:02.000 --> 00:10:03.320
I just want to ask you.

00:10:04.670 --> 00:10:06.950
Do you know

00:10:06.950 --> 00:10:07.790
where Meng Qin hid that?

00:10:08.710 --> 00:10:09.510
Hid what?

00:10:09.950 --> 00:10:10.840
I don't know.

00:10:12.040 --> 00:10:14.240
Makes sense. He wouldn't tell you

00:10:15.040 --> 00:10:16.840
something so important to keep it a secret.

00:10:17.240 --> 00:10:17.630
Okay.

00:10:18.360 --> 00:10:19.270
Then let me ask you.

00:10:20.190 --> 00:10:21.560
Do you know where Meng Qin is?

00:10:24.880 --> 00:10:26.510
Don't blame me

00:10:26.550 --> 00:10:27.630
if you don't know anything.

00:10:29.070 --> 00:10:29.790
Guys.

00:10:29.790 --> 00:10:30.500
Yes.

00:10:31.190 --> 00:10:33.320
You have to find it even if

00:10:33.710 --> 00:10:35.840
you have to dig through the ground.

00:10:36.040 --> 00:10:37.120
- Yes, sir. Get in. - Yes, sir.

00:10:38.400 --> 00:10:38.990
What's going on?

00:10:41.910 --> 00:10:42.990
They're not in the dungeon.

00:10:43.070 --> 00:10:43.910
All we know is that

00:10:44.070 --> 00:10:46.200
someone did break into the Chamber of Commerce yesterday.

00:10:46.640 --> 00:10:49.030
Looks like Feng Qianli's in a bad way.

00:10:50.830 --> 00:10:51.720
There's one more piece of news.

00:10:52.430 --> 00:10:53.360
Meng Qin's family was taken away

00:10:53.360 --> 00:10:54.790
by Sun Siming this morning.

00:10:55.280 --> 00:10:55.790
Taken away?

00:10:57.000 --> 00:10:57.600
Let's save them.

00:10:58.520 --> 00:10:59.550
Do you know where they are?

00:10:59.550 --> 00:11:00.120
Why in such a hurry?

00:11:00.120 --> 00:11:00.790
They must be in the Meng's.

00:11:02.550 --> 00:11:03.150
Young Mistress.

00:11:03.910 --> 00:11:04.710
I've done the favor

00:11:04.710 --> 00:11:05.480
you asked me to do,

00:11:05.670 --> 00:11:06.510
so you have to come back with me.

00:11:07.480 --> 00:11:08.480
Jiu.

00:11:28.040 --> 00:11:29.360
Chairman, nothing.

00:11:35.400 --> 00:11:37.480
As the old saying goes, one can't bring a disaster to the family.

00:11:38.240 --> 00:11:39.990
He should take responsibility.

00:11:41.280 --> 00:11:42.360
This has nothing

00:11:42.520 --> 00:11:44.120
to do with you,

00:11:44.910 --> 00:11:46.390
but I despise people

00:11:46.480 --> 00:11:47.870
who don't care about their families

00:11:48.400 --> 00:11:50.670
when things go wrong.

00:11:50.910 --> 00:11:53.390
Madam, I'm so sad for you.

00:11:55.950 --> 00:11:56.960
Meng Qin.

00:11:58.120 --> 00:11:59.790
Since you're shameless,

00:12:00.520 --> 00:12:02.360
I'll do as you wish.

00:12:03.910 --> 00:12:05.840
Strip her naked

00:12:06.830 --> 00:12:07.630
and leave her at the door

00:12:08.360 --> 00:12:10.360
for all his neighbors to see.

00:12:11.360 --> 00:12:12.910
The backbone of the Meng family,

00:12:13.240 --> 00:12:14.480
the hero.

00:12:14.790 --> 00:12:16.960
Put her clothes on

00:12:17.190 --> 00:12:19.030
when Meng Qin appears.

00:12:19.360 --> 00:12:19.960
Let go of me.

00:12:21.590 --> 00:12:24.030
Don't bully my mother.

00:12:25.040 --> 00:12:27.720
Help me. Let go of him.

00:12:28.480 --> 00:12:29.560
Hang her up.

00:12:38.400 --> 00:12:38.960
See?

00:12:39.950 --> 00:12:41.910
Wouldn't it have been fine if you'd shown up earlier?

00:12:42.000 --> 00:12:43.630
Why do you make me do things I don't want to do?

00:12:44.040 --> 00:12:44.630
Honey.

00:12:45.430 --> 00:12:47.200
Just give them whatever they want.

00:12:48.310 --> 00:12:50.600
I haven't begged you in all these years.

00:12:51.950 --> 00:12:52.870
Just give it to him.

00:12:53.360 --> 00:12:54.960
Madam is right.

00:12:59.440 --> 00:13:01.320
Why is he in such a hurry?

00:13:01.830 --> 00:13:02.560
Exactly.

00:13:11.310 --> 00:13:12.510
Hello, My Lord.

00:13:13.120 --> 00:13:13.670
My Lord.

00:13:14.400 --> 00:13:15.240
Did you call us here

00:13:15.590 --> 00:13:16.960
to discuss something important?

00:13:17.120 --> 00:13:18.000
I'm traveling

00:13:18.240 --> 00:13:19.880
to Xichuan in a few days.

00:13:20.930 --> 00:13:22.340
When I leave Jibei,

00:13:22.400 --> 00:13:23.840
I'll have peace of mind

00:13:24.070 --> 00:13:25.390
if you can handle the affairs

00:13:25.760 --> 00:13:26.670
of the royal household.

00:13:27.550 --> 00:13:28.750
My Lord, don't worry.

00:13:28.880 --> 00:13:30.720
We will do our best.

00:13:31.910 --> 00:13:35.120
Liu Luan may not be on our side anymore,

00:13:35.360 --> 00:13:37.870
but I have taken control of him with Japonicus.

00:13:38.040 --> 00:13:39.120
When I go to Xichuan,

00:13:39.550 --> 00:13:41.030
I will take him with me

00:13:41.590 --> 00:13:43.300
to prevent him from interfering in the government.

00:13:44.790 --> 00:13:46.390
After I leave, Sage Can,

00:13:47.240 --> 00:13:50.360
please take care of the treasury and taxes.

00:13:51.040 --> 00:13:51.960
Yes, sir.

00:13:52.430 --> 00:13:53.200
Sage Mao.

00:13:54.120 --> 00:13:55.910
You recommended Du Shang,

00:13:56.280 --> 00:13:57.200
and he helped me a lot.

00:13:57.430 --> 00:13:58.790
I'll leave the military affairs

00:13:58.950 --> 00:14:03.630
to you and Sage Kui.

00:14:03.790 --> 00:14:05.080
Yes, sir.

00:14:19.950 --> 00:14:20.840
I'll drink tea

00:14:21.760 --> 00:14:22.840
to the three of you.

00:14:23.160 --> 00:14:24.150
It's our job.

00:14:24.430 --> 00:14:26.030
You're welcome, My Lord.

00:14:26.160 --> 00:14:28.790
We await your triumph.

00:14:58.360 --> 00:14:59.360
I've hidden the Painting of Luan

00:15:00.520 --> 00:15:02.320
in a hut in the mountains outside the city.

00:15:03.190 --> 00:15:04.670
Enter the mountains from the north entrance,

00:15:05.360 --> 00:15:06.030
cross three hills,

00:15:06.400 --> 00:15:07.320
go west for a mile,

00:15:07.880 --> 00:15:08.560
and go north when you

00:15:09.040 --> 00:15:09.720
meet the fork in the road.

00:15:10.400 --> 00:15:11.270
Then you will see the hut.

00:15:11.760 --> 00:15:13.440
Just in case you're lying to me,

00:15:14.280 --> 00:15:14.960
please

00:15:15.550 --> 00:15:17.270
take us there.

00:15:40.910 --> 00:15:42.440
It seems we are late after all.

00:15:57.910 --> 00:15:58.510
Fu Sheng.

00:15:59.400 --> 00:16:00.030
Look at this.

00:16:07.940 --> 00:16:11.710
[Xichuan]

00:16:11.710 --> 00:16:13.150
It's a different color inside.

00:16:13.760 --> 00:16:15.080
It should have just been carved.

00:16:15.710 --> 00:16:17.000
I think this should be the clue

00:16:17.000 --> 00:16:18.080
Meng Qin left us.

00:16:18.840 --> 00:16:20.140
What kind of clue is it?

00:16:24.670 --> 00:16:25.390
It's a map.

00:16:33.360 --> 00:16:34.950
I didn't realize you

00:16:34.950 --> 00:16:36.440
had such a large courtyard here,

00:16:39.120 --> 00:16:40.270
but I don't know

00:16:41.520 --> 00:16:43.030
if there's an ambush here.

00:16:43.480 --> 00:16:45.440
Cut the crap. Let go of me.

00:16:45.440 --> 00:16:46.240
I'll take you in.

00:16:47.070 --> 00:16:48.200
It's inside.

00:16:51.190 --> 00:16:52.270
Are there

00:16:52.520 --> 00:16:54.360
any traps in here?

00:16:55.280 --> 00:16:55.790
No.

00:16:58.070 --> 00:16:58.670
If you

00:16:59.710 --> 00:17:01.390
hadn't been willing to bring me here,

00:17:01.710 --> 00:17:02.750
I might have been more at ease,

00:17:03.480 --> 00:17:05.630
but you've been walking so smoothly

00:17:05.630 --> 00:17:06.710
and in such a hurry all this way,

00:17:07.790 --> 00:17:10.150
so your mind is so obvious that even a fool can see it.

00:17:11.720 --> 00:17:12.600
Are you afraid?

00:17:13.680 --> 00:17:14.080
How about this?

00:17:15.350 --> 00:17:16.560
You, go in and get

00:17:17.240 --> 00:17:18.520
the Painting of Luan with him.

00:17:18.830 --> 00:17:19.520
I will wait for you

00:17:20.310 --> 00:17:22.230
outside with your wife and children.

00:17:22.680 --> 00:17:24.800
When you give me the Painting of Luan,

00:17:24.830 --> 00:17:26.710
I'll return your wife and child to you.

00:17:30.480 --> 00:17:31.000
Go.

00:17:39.070 --> 00:17:41.510
Now that you're married to him,

00:17:41.720 --> 00:17:42.520
accept what happens.

00:17:43.390 --> 00:17:44.360
It's your destiny.

00:17:50.320 --> 00:17:51.290
Surely, there is a trap.

00:17:53.480 --> 00:17:54.360
Meng Qin.

00:17:55.830 --> 00:17:58.040
Don't you care about the lives of your wife and child?

00:18:00.440 --> 00:18:02.360
I will kill them.

00:18:11.720 --> 00:18:12.320
Kill them.

00:18:16.870 --> 00:18:18.840
Please spare my life.

00:18:44.000 --> 00:18:45.000
Got the painting?

00:18:47.200 --> 00:18:48.080
Chairman Guo.

00:18:49.520 --> 00:18:50.630
This guy is so cunning.

00:18:50.630 --> 00:18:51.670
I almost had it.

00:18:52.110 --> 00:18:53.280
Which means you didn't get it?

00:18:54.200 --> 00:18:56.320
Thank you for saving my life.

00:18:57.350 --> 00:18:58.600
I don't have it now,

00:18:59.040 --> 00:19:00.710
but I have a countermeasure.

00:19:10.110 --> 00:19:10.710
Meng Qin.

00:19:14.960 --> 00:19:15.630
He's still breathing.

00:19:15.630 --> 00:19:16.280
Help him up.

00:19:31.110 --> 00:19:31.670
Meng Qin.

00:19:32.350 --> 00:19:33.390
Is that Sun Siming?

00:19:36.070 --> 00:19:40.040
Save my wife and son.

00:19:42.590 --> 00:19:43.390
It's too late.

00:19:46.720 --> 00:19:47.630
Tell me.

00:19:48.000 --> 00:19:49.020
Where's the map you said you'd use

00:19:49.040 --> 00:19:50.360
to decipher the mechanism?

00:19:50.720 --> 00:19:53.520
I am sorry.

00:19:54.140 --> 00:19:56.200
I lied to you

00:19:56.550 --> 00:19:58.760
to save my wife and son.

00:19:59.440 --> 00:20:02.280
There's...

00:20:02.480 --> 00:20:04.340
There's no map.

00:20:05.590 --> 00:20:06.640
What did I say?

00:20:07.630 --> 00:20:09.600
It's all a lie, but you don't believe me.

00:20:10.680 --> 00:20:12.670
Painting...

00:20:13.070 --> 00:20:14.360
Painting of Luan.

00:20:15.310 --> 00:20:18.190
The bucket at the bottom of the well.

00:20:19.150 --> 00:20:20.120
I didn't...

00:20:20.520 --> 00:20:24.870
I didn't tell them where it really is.

00:20:28.720 --> 00:20:31.280
You. Run.

00:20:31.830 --> 00:20:33.490
He'll kill you

00:20:33.790 --> 00:20:36.300
after he

00:20:36.440 --> 00:20:38.760
gets the painting.

00:20:45.790 --> 00:20:46.430
Put him down.

00:21:21.440 --> 00:21:22.520
Is this the Painting of Luan?

00:21:25.830 --> 00:21:28.150
[Painting of Luan's hiding place]
No, it's not.

00:21:28.280 --> 00:21:30.190
This is the real hiding place of the Painting of Luan.

00:21:32.440 --> 00:21:33.520
It seems a dying man

00:21:33.520 --> 00:21:34.360
speaks the truth.

00:21:35.390 --> 00:21:37.040
This time, he's not fooling us.

00:21:38.310 --> 00:21:40.710
He just said we should run

00:21:41.480 --> 00:21:43.840
because he was afraid Sun Siming would kill me

00:21:43.840 --> 00:21:44.430
for the Bird Jade Plate.

00:21:46.000 --> 00:21:46.430
Let's go.

00:21:48.150 --> 00:21:49.040
You'd better not go.

00:21:49.870 --> 00:21:51.280
I think Sun Siming

00:21:51.280 --> 00:21:52.150
is ambushing us nearby.

00:21:53.760 --> 00:21:54.840
Then I have to go.

00:21:55.440 --> 00:21:56.800
Nerds like you can't fight.

00:21:57.720 --> 00:21:59.150
With your Ghost Needle,

00:21:59.720 --> 00:22:01.430
you might turn into a ghost.

00:22:02.440 --> 00:22:03.080
Don't worry.

00:22:04.440 --> 00:22:05.800
I've had nothing but luck

00:22:06.440 --> 00:22:07.120
in my life.

00:22:08.310 --> 00:22:09.000
Take the time

00:22:09.310 --> 00:22:10.360
to read what it says.

00:22:12.870 --> 00:22:15.040
The sun travels west, and the pavilion appears.

00:22:15.280 --> 00:22:16.950
The grass is sparse on the hillside.

00:22:17.110 --> 00:22:18.040
What does that mean?

00:22:18.490 --> 00:22:19.620
The sun travels west.

00:22:22.040 --> 00:22:23.150
It's just right now.

00:22:24.520 --> 00:22:27.120
The pavilion.

00:22:29.590 --> 00:22:30.120
There.

00:22:39.440 --> 00:22:40.430
What else does it say?

00:22:44.480 --> 00:22:46.520
Green bamboo leaves, the Xuan shines.

00:22:47.980 --> 00:22:49.890
The red in the green indicates its location.

00:22:51.870 --> 00:22:54.280
"Green bamboo leaves" refers to this bamboo forest.

00:22:54.720 --> 00:22:55.920
Xuan

00:22:57.000 --> 00:22:58.640
means Luan.

00:22:58.720 --> 00:23:01.040
So the Painting of Luan is here.

00:23:01.310 --> 00:23:03.190
How are we supposed to find it in such a big bamboo forest?

00:23:03.480 --> 00:23:04.950
It also says "red in the green".

00:23:05.720 --> 00:23:06.870
Where's the red color

00:23:07.280 --> 00:23:08.120
in all this green?

00:23:09.920 --> 00:23:10.930
Let's split up and look for it.

00:23:11.070 --> 00:23:11.630
I'll go there.

00:23:11.790 --> 00:23:12.280
You go there.

00:23:29.070 --> 00:23:30.710
Red in the green.

00:23:33.350 --> 00:23:34.800
Gu Tian, I found it.

00:23:52.790 --> 00:23:54.080
"Red in the green"

00:23:55.040 --> 00:23:56.230
must be this spot.

00:23:56.720 --> 00:23:57.910
I'll dig.

00:23:58.070 --> 00:23:59.110
I don't want

00:23:59.110 --> 00:24:01.800
to burden you with this physical labor.

00:24:16.350 --> 00:24:19.320
Painting of Luan? Shouldn't this be Ball of Luan?

00:24:20.040 --> 00:24:21.280
You're a disaster for me.

00:24:22.000 --> 00:24:23.430
I always said my life

00:24:23.430 --> 00:24:24.670
would be lost because of you.

00:24:25.390 --> 00:24:27.040
Looks like it's going to come true this time.

00:24:28.310 --> 00:24:29.150
I'm sorry.

00:24:30.520 --> 00:24:31.320
Fu Sheng.

00:24:32.110 --> 00:24:33.720
The Bird Jade Plate has always been

00:24:33.720 --> 00:24:34.680
with you,

00:24:34.830 --> 00:24:36.280
but you never mentioned it.

00:24:36.590 --> 00:24:38.560
You didn't think of me as a friend.

00:24:39.920 --> 00:24:42.450
The people who were your friends are dead.

00:24:42.590 --> 00:24:44.000
