00:24:44.720 --> 00:24:46.200
I've always treated you

00:24:46.200 --> 00:24:47.430
like brothers.

00:24:48.550 --> 00:24:50.070
Have I ever refused to help you

00:24:50.070 --> 00:24:51.520
when you came to me?

00:24:52.240 --> 00:24:54.280
But when it comes to the Treasure of the Sealed Book,

00:24:54.480 --> 00:24:56.280
you just care about making money

00:24:56.550 --> 00:24:57.430
and never mentioned it to me.

00:24:58.680 --> 00:24:59.840
I'm disappointed.

00:25:02.040 --> 00:25:02.760
Cut the crap.

00:25:03.720 --> 00:25:04.430
Get down to business.

00:25:07.310 --> 00:25:08.040
See?

00:25:08.590 --> 00:25:10.320
