00:25:58.720 --> 00:26:00.080
Still want me to keep the jade plate for you?

00:26:00.520 --> 00:26:00.950
Take it.

00:26:02.630 --> 00:26:03.670
You take it.

00:26:03.830 --> 00:26:04.710
It's more secure.

00:26:07.680 --> 00:26:08.150
That makes sense.

00:26:22.200 --> 00:26:22.800
Kill them.

00:26:24.280 --> 00:26:24.910
Kill them?

00:26:26.760 --> 00:26:27.840
These two know too much,

00:26:28.520 --> 00:26:29.280
so we need to prevent future problems.

00:26:31.200 --> 00:26:33.080
But we haven't found the Bird Jade Plate.

00:26:33.390 --> 00:26:35.230
It must be in that clinic

00:26:36.000 --> 00:26:36.840
or

00:26:37.830 --> 00:26:39.760
with that little girl from the Lord's Mansion.

00:26:43.040 --> 00:26:44.080
I got you, didn't I?

00:26:46.200 --> 00:26:46.800
Do it.

00:26:47.760 --> 00:26:48.280
Actually,

00:26:48.350 --> 00:26:48.760
Chairman Guo,

00:26:49.550 --> 00:26:50.430
I owe

00:26:50.920 --> 00:26:52.190
Fu Sheng a favor,

00:26:53.280 --> 00:26:54.840
so could you spare their lives

00:26:56.110 --> 00:26:56.840
for my sake?

00:27:00.630 --> 00:27:01.710
For your sake?

00:27:03.440 --> 00:27:04.390
Who do you think you are?

00:27:06.070 --> 00:27:07.600
If you can't find the Bird Jade Plate,

00:27:10.310 --> 00:27:11.320
you won't live either.

00:27:25.240 --> 00:27:26.040
My friends.

00:27:26.870 --> 00:27:27.710
You saw it.

00:27:28.720 --> 00:27:30.150
That's all I can do for you,

00:27:30.630 --> 00:27:31.560
