00:27:35.200 --> 00:27:36.840
And I'll bring with me one,

00:27:37.240 --> 00:27:38.520
sorry, two jars of good wine.

00:27:39.440 --> 00:27:40.120
Rest in peace,

00:27:42.520 --> 00:27:43.840
friends.

00:27:44.760 --> 00:27:45.720
Wait a minute.

00:27:46.880 --> 00:27:47.810
I have something to say.

00:27:48.830 --> 00:27:51.280
Fu Sheng, before we die,

00:27:52.590 --> 00:27:53.800
